*** Create react app using npx

npx create-react-app react-counter

**** Output 

Creating a new React app in /home/boring/frontend/react/react-counter.

Installing packages. This might take a couple of minutes.
Installing react, react-dom, and react-scripts with cra-template...


***** Start the react app

npm run start


**** git commands to push the files to github

git commit -m "first commit"
git remote add origin git@github.com:gprathi/react-counter.git
git push -u origin master

